# Deutsch-Jozsa Formal Verification

This repository contains the Rocq implementation accompanying the Honours dissertation.

The work formalises the Deutsch-Jozsa algorithm, oracle assumptions, correctness properties and later extends to Grover's search algorithm.

Current Progress

✓ Bitstring definitions

✓ Oracle definitions

✓ Promise definitions

□ DJ correctness proof

□ Grover verification

Currently as of 3/7/26, the majority of the frameworks has proofs written as Admitted. This is only a placeholder for building but they will be replaced by actual ROCQ proofs as the project progresses